        {
            "title": "William Blair因競爭壓力加劇下調Adobe評級",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - William Blair週四在一份報告中將<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Adobe\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Adobe;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Adobe\">Adobe</a>評級下調至市場表現級,理由是該公司核心Creative Cloud業務面臨「激烈競爭」,其長期競爭地位的不確定性日益上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Arjun Bhatia表示,他將獨立負責<span><span>Adobe</span></span>的研究覆蓋,並解釋稱,儘管該股票僅以9倍自由現金流交易,「我們主要擔憂的是Adobe面臨的激烈競爭。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據William Blair稱,競爭環境引發了關於Adobe定價能力、差異化能力以及其「贏得AI機遇的權利」的「合理質疑」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e7ea225b-fedd-3eca-b40e-887dc8deadb3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bhatia強調:「需要明確的是,我們並非將Adobe稱為『AI輸家』……但承認這些問題的未知答案可能會使該股至少維持區間震盪。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司強調,AI如何「在一夜之間,將創意專業人士所建立的高度技術性技能民主化」,加速了來自Canva和Figma等競爭對手已經形成的壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Canva的年度經常性收入已達到40億美元,增長超過30%,而Figma的運營規模為12億美元,擴張40%,相比之下,Adobe規模大得多但增長較慢的數位媒體業務為190億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bhatia還指出了快速增長的「AI原生」競爭對手,包括Midjourney、Runway和StabilityAI,以及Google、OpenAI和Apple等主要平台日益增長的興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然現在挑選長期贏家還為時過早,但William Blair警告稱,Adobe「非常健康的40%多的營業利潤率」可能會吸引進一步的競爭侵蝕,並補充說利潤率趨勢和公司捕捉AI驅動新需求的能力「應受到監控」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/william-blair%E5%9B%A0%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BFadobe%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-123352235.html",
