        },
        {
            "title": "10家銀行挺記憶體龍頭！臺銀統籌威剛120億聯貸案 超額認購2.1倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JkuP6Sxk69Yn5OtlsvmCLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f4e8eceb93aa9ad922f06c7608a9b791\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/10%E5%AE%B6%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8C%BA%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94%E9%BE%8D%E9%A0%AD-%E8%87%BA%E9%8A%80%E7%B5%B1%E7%B1%8C%E5%A8%81%E5%89%9B120%E5%84%84%E8%81%AF%E8%B2%B8%E6%A1%88-%E8%B6%85%E9%A1%8D%E8%AA%8D%E8%B3%BC2-1%E5%80%8D-112615667.html",
